      "content": "Hey, the board is pushing for a new policy. They want to implement a \"Human Oversight Layer\" where a diverse committee of managers reviews every mortgage application we decline. They think it'll help catch systemic bias. Give me your take on this. Is this actually going to help our accuracy?",
